<span id="an_8:19">8:19</span> And Jakim, and Zichri, and Zabdi,

<span id="an_8:20">8:20</span> and Elienai, and Zillethai, and Eliel,

<span id="an_8:21">8:21</span> and Adaiah, and Beraiah, and Shimrath,
