<span id="an_8:22">8:22</span> And Ishpan, and Heber, and Eliel,

<span id="an_8:23">8:23</span> and Abdon, and Zichri, and Hanan,

<span id="an_8:24">8:24</span> and Hananiah, and Elam, and Antothijah,

<span id="an_8:25">8:25</span> and Iphedeiah, and Penuel, sons of
