<span id="an_9:40">9:40</span> And a son of Jonathan \[is\] Merib-Baal,
and Merib-Baal begat Micah.

<span id="an_9:41">9:41</span> And sons of Micah: Pithon, and Melech,
and Tahrea,

<span id="an_9:42">9:42</span> and Ahaz -- he begat Jaarah, and Jaarah
